  <num>47-2205</num>
  <heading>Payment of tax by purchaser.</heading>
  <text>If a purchaser has not reimbursed for the tax such vendors or retailers as are required or authorized to pay the tax, as the case may be, such purchaser shall file a return as hereinafter provided and pay to the Mayor a tax at the rates provided in <cite path="§47-2002">§ 47-2002</cite> on the sales prices of property and services purchased at retail sale.</text>
